2
00:00:01,102 --> 00:00:02,981
20th July 1969,

3
00:00:02,981 --> 00:00:06,616
The Lunar Module of the Apollo 11 mission landed on the moon.

4
00:00:07,217 --> 00:00:10,715
Astronauts Neil Armstrong and Buzz Aldrin were in it.

5
00:00:10,715 --> 00:00:14,527
After the landing, Neil Armstrong tried to open the door,

6
00:00:14,527 --> 00:00:16,029
to get down on the moon.

7
00:00:16,029 --> 00:00:18,005
It wasn't easy opening this door,

8
00:00:18,005 --> 00:00:19,277
due to high pressure,

9
00:00:19,277 --> 00:00:22,275
but he successfully opened it after a little struggle.

10
00:00:22,275 --> 00:00:27,505
Then he tried to get down to the moon in his heavy spacesuit.

11
00:00:27,505 --> 00:00:29,785
The exit wasn't spacious

12
00:00:29,785 --> 00:00:34,730
so by mistake, he hit the top, and a piece of the Lunar Module broke off.

13
00:00:35,197 --> 00:00:36,995
Neither of them was aware of this

14
00:00:36,995 --> 00:00:38,673
because of the lack of air.

15
00:00:38,673 --> 00:00:40,910
The sound didn't travel.

16
00:00:40,910 --> 00:00:42,511
They didn't hear any sound.

17
00:00:42,511 --> 00:00:45,951
But this broken piece was very crucial.

18
00:00:45,951 --> 00:00:48,567
It was the Assent Engine Arming Switch.

19
00:00:48,567 --> 00:00:52,855
Without this switch, their Lunar Module couldn't take off again,

20
00:00:52,855 --> 00:00:55,440
and they couldn't return to Earth.

21
00:00:55,440 --> 00:00:58,483
Unaware of this, Neil Armstrong got out

22
00:00:58,483 --> 00:01:00,439
and stepped on the moon's surface.

23
00:01:00,439 --> 00:01:04,081
He became the first man to step on the moon.

24
00:01:04,081 --> 00:01:06,464
"One small step for man,

25
00:01:07,120 --> 00:01:09,344
one giant leap for mankind."

26
00:01:13,280 --> 00:01:15,214
But did it actually happen?

27
00:01:15,214 --> 00:01:18,032
Today, more than 50 years later,

28
00:01:18,032 --> 00:01:22,374
many people refuse to believe that humans had gone to the moon.

29
00:01:22,374 --> 00:01:25,098
People cook up theories of their own

30
00:01:25,098 --> 00:01:30,106
to claim that the entire Apollo 11 mission was a farce put up by America.

31
00:01:30,106 --> 00:01:32,698
That they filmed the scenes on Earth,

32
00:01:32,698 --> 00:01:34,174
and lied to the world.

33
00:01:34,174 --> 00:01:37,365
How else do you explain the flag fluttering without air?

34
00:01:37,365 --> 00:01:39,062
What's the truth to it?

35
00:01:39,062 --> 00:01:41,456
Come let's try to understand this story

36
00:01:41,456 --> 00:01:42,918
in today's video.

37
